### 4. Routing (React Router v7 file-based)

#### [NEW] `app/routes/`

```
app/routes/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ _index.tsx              вҶ’ Home
в”ңв”Җв”Җ reformas-integrales-madrid.tsx
в”ңв”Җв”Җ reformas-cocinas-madrid.tsx
в”ңв”Җв”Җ reformas-banos-madrid.tsx
в”ңв”Җв”Җ reformas-madrid.$barrio.tsx  вҶ’ Landing por barrio (dinГЎmico)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ proyectos.tsx
в”ңв”Җв”Җ blog._index.tsx
в”ңв”Җв”Җ blog.$slug.tsx
в”ңв”Җв”Җ contacto.tsx
в”ңв”Җв”Җ sobre-nosotros.tsx
```

Cada route file importa su template + carga datos del cliente.

